#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating an Account"
msgstr "Δημιουργώντας ένα λογαριασμό "

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:176
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
